OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBiggest UK pub chain to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcharge more at peak hours  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The pub group that owns Slug & Lettuce 
OL,6, and Yates's bars has said it will      
OL,7, charge about 20p more per pint during  
OL,8, peak hours due to cost increases.      
OL,10,FStonegate Group, the UK's biggest pub  
OL,11,Fchain, says 800 of its 4,000 pubs will 
OL,12,Fintroduce "dynamic pricing" during     
OL,13,Fevenings and weekends.                 
OL,15,FIt said the price rise reflected the   
OL,16,Fhigher costs the company was facing,   
OL,17,Fincluding extra security.              
OL,19,FPeak-time pricing is used by other     
OL,20,Fsectors like travel when demand spikes.
